{
  "text": [
    {
      "text": [
        {
          "text": "An oracle concerning Nineveh. The book of the vision of Nahum of Elkosh.",
          "ID": "1"
        },
        {
          "text": "The Lord is a jealous and avenging God;",
          "ID": "2"
        },
        {
          "text": "the Lord is avenging and wrathful;",
          "ID": "2"
        },
        {
          "text": "the Lord takes vengeance on his adversaries",
          "ID": "2"
        },
        {
          "text": "and keeps wrath for his enemies.",
          "ID": "2"
        },
        {
          "text": "The Lord is slow to anger and great in power,",
          "ID": "3"
        },
        {
          "text": "and the Lord will by no means clear the guilty.",
          "ID": "3"
        },
        {
          "text": "His way is in whirlwind and storm,",
          "ID": "3"
        },
        {
          "text": "and the clouds are the dust of his feet.",
          "ID": "3"
        },
        {
          "text": "He rebukes the sea and makes it dry;",
          "ID": "4"
        },
        {
          "text": "he dries up all the rivers;",
          "ID": "4"
        },
        {
          "text": "Bashan and Carmel wither;",
          "ID": "4"
        },
        {
          "text": "the bloom of Lebanon withers.",
          "ID": "4"
        },
        {
          "text": "The mountains quake before him;",
          "ID": "5"
        },
        {
          "text": "the hills melt;",
          "ID": "5"
        },
        {
          "text": "the earth heaves before him,",
          "ID": "5"
        },
        {
          "text": "the world and all who dwell in it.",
          "ID": "5"
        },
        {
          "text": "Who can stand before his indignation?",
          "ID": "6"
        },
        {
          "text": "Who can endure the heat of his anger?",
          "ID": "6"
        },
        {
          "text": "His wrath is poured out like fire,",
          "ID": "6"
        },
        {
          "text": "and the rocks are broken into pieces by him.",
          "ID": "6"
        },
        {
          "text": "The Lord is good,",
          "ID": "7"
        },
        {
          "text": "a stronghold in the day of trouble;",
          "ID": "7"
        },
        {
          "text": "he knows those who take refuge in him.",
          "ID": "7"
        },
        {
          "text": "But with an overflowing flood",
          "ID": "8"
        },
        {
          "text": "he will make a complete end of the adversaries,",
          "ID": "8"
        },
        {
          "text": "and will pursue his enemies into darkness.",
          "ID": "8"
        },
        {
          "text": "What do you plot against the Lord?",
          "ID": "9"
        },
        {
          "text": "He will make a complete end;",
          "ID": "9"
        },
        {
          "text": "trouble will not rise up a second time.",
          "ID": "9"
        },
        {
          "text": "For they are like entangled thorns,",
          "ID": "10"
        },
        {
          "text": "like drunkards as they drink;",
          "ID": "10"
        },
        {
          "text": "they are consumed like stubble fully dried.",
          "ID": "10"
        },
        {
          "text": "From you came one",
          "ID": "11"
        },
        {
          "text": "who plotted evil against the Lord,",
          "ID": "11"
        },
        {
          "text": "a worthless counselor.",
          "ID": "11"
        },
        {
          "text": "Thus says the Lord,",
          "ID": "12"
        },
        {
          "text": "\"Though they are at full strength and many,",
          "ID": "12"
        },
        {
          "text": "they will be cut down and pass away.",
          "ID": "12"
        },
        {
          "text": "Though I have afflicted you,",
          "ID": "12"
        },
        {
          "text": "I will afflict you no more.",
          "ID": "12"
        },
        {
          "text": "And now I will break his yoke from off you",
          "ID": "13"
        },
        {
          "text": "and will burst your bonds apart.\"",
          "ID": "13"
        },
        {
          "text": "The Lord has given commandment about you:",
          "ID": "14"
        },
        {
          "text": "\"No more shall your name be perpetuated;",
          "ID": "14"
        },
        {
          "text": "from the house of your gods I will cut off",
          "ID": "14"
        },
        {
          "text": "the carved image and the metal image.",
          "ID": "14"
        },
        {
          "text": "I will make your grave, for you are vile.\"",
          "ID": "14"
        },
        {
          "text": "Behold, upon the mountains, the feet of him",
          "ID": "15"
        },
        {
          "text": "who brings good news,",
          "ID": "15"
        },
        {
          "text": "who publishes peace!",
          "ID": "15"
        },
        {
          "text": "Keep your feasts, O Judah;",
          "ID": "15"
        },
        {
          "text": "fulfill your vows,",
          "ID": "15"
        },
        {
          "text": "for never again shall the worthless pass through you;",
          "ID": "15"
        },
        {
          "text": "he is utterly cut off.",
          "ID": "15"
        }
      ],
      "ID": "OT:NAM.1",
      "name": "Nahum 1"
    },
    {
      "text": [
        {
          "text": "The scatterer has come up against you.",
          "ID": "1"
        },
        {
          "text": "Man the ramparts;",
          "ID": "1"
        },
        {
          "text": "watch the road;",
          "ID": "1"
        },
        {
          "text": "dress for battle;",
          "ID": "1"
        },
        {
          "text": "collect all your strength.",
          "ID": "1"
        },
        {
          "text": "For the Lord is restoring the majesty of Jacob",
          "ID": "2"
        },
        {
          "text": "as the majesty of Israel,",
          "ID": "2"
        },
        {
          "text": "for plunderers have plundered them",
          "ID": "2"
        },
        {
          "text": "and ruined their branches.",
          "ID": "2"
        },
        {
          "text": "The shield of his mighty men is red;",
          "ID": "3"
        },
        {
          "text": "his soldiers are clothed in scarlet.",
          "ID": "3"
        },
        {
          "text": "The chariots come with flashing metal",
          "ID": "3"
        },
        {
          "text": "on the day he musters them;",
          "ID": "3"
        },
        {
          "text": "the cypress spears are brandished.",
          "ID": "3"
        },
        {
          "text": "The chariots race madly through the streets;",
          "ID": "4"
        },
        {
          "text": "they rush to and fro through the squares;",
          "ID": "4"
        },
        {
          "text": "they gleam like torches;",
          "ID": "4"
        },
        {
          "text": "they dart like lightning.",
          "ID": "4"
        },
        {
          "text": "He remembers his officers;",
          "ID": "5"
        },
        {
          "text": "they stumble as they go,",
          "ID": "5"
        },
        {
          "text": "they hasten to the wall;",
          "ID": "5"
        },
        {
          "text": "the siege tower is set up.",
          "ID": "5"
        },
        {
          "text": "The river gates are opened;",
          "ID": "6"
        },
        {
          "text": "the palace melts away;",
          "ID": "6"
        },
        {
          "text": "its mistress is stripped; she is carried off,",
          "ID": "7"
        },
        {
          "text": "her slave girls lamenting,",
          "ID": "7"
        },
        {
          "text": "moaning like doves",
          "ID": "7"
        },
        {
          "text": "and beating their breasts.",
          "ID": "7"
        },
        {
          "text": "Nineveh is like a pool",
          "ID": "8"
        },
        {
          "text": "whose waters run away.",
          "ID": "8"
        },
        {
          "text": "\"Halt! Halt!\" they cry,",
          "ID": "8"
        },
        {
          "text": "but none turns back.",
          "ID": "8"
        },
        {
          "text": "Plunder the silver,",
          "ID": "9"
        },
        {
          "text": "plunder the gold!",
          "ID": "9"
        },
        {
          "text": "There is no end of the treasure",
          "ID": "9"
        },
        {
          "text": "or of the wealth of all precious things.",
          "ID": "9"
        },
        {
          "text": "Desolate! Desolation and ruin!",
          "ID": "10"
        },
        {
          "text": "Hearts melt and knees tremble;",
          "ID": "10"
        },
        {
          "text": "anguish is in all loins;",
          "ID": "10"
        },
        {
          "text": "all faces grow pale!",
          "ID": "10"
        },
        {
          "text": "Where is the lions' den,",
          "ID": "11"
        },
        {
          "text": "the feeding place of the young lions,",
          "ID": "11"
        },
        {
          "text": "where the lion and lioness went,",
          "ID": "11"
        },
        {
          "text": "where his cubs were, with none to disturb?",
          "ID": "11"
        },
        {
          "text": "The lion tore enough for his cubs",
          "ID": "12"
        },
        {
          "text": "and strangled prey for his lionesses;",
          "ID": "12"
        },
        {
          "text": "he filled his caves with prey",
          "ID": "12"
        },
        {
          "text": "and his dens with torn flesh.",
          "ID": "12"
        },
        {
          "text": "Behold, I am against you, declares the Lord of hosts, and I will burn your chariots in smoke, and the sword shall devour your young lions. I will cut off your prey from the earth, and the voice of your messengers shall no longer be heard.",
          "ID": "13"
        }
      ],
      "ID": "OT:NAM.2",
      "name": "Nahum 2"
    },
    {
      "text": [
        {
          "text": "Woe to the bloody city,",
          "ID": "1"
        },
        {
          "text": "all full of lies and plunder—",
          "ID": "1"
        },
        {
          "text": "no end to the prey!",
          "ID": "1"
        },
        {
          "text": "The crack of the whip, and rumble of the wheel,",
          "ID": "2"
        },
        {
          "text": "galloping horse and bounding chariot!",
          "ID": "2"
        },
        {
          "text": "Horsemen charging,",
          "ID": "3"
        },
        {
          "text": "flashing sword and glittering spear,",
          "ID": "3"
        },
        {
          "text": "hosts of slain,",
          "ID": "3"
        },
        {
          "text": "heaps of corpses,",
          "ID": "3"
        },
        {
          "text": "dead bodies without end—",
          "ID": "3"
        },
        {
          "text": "they stumble over the bodies!",
          "ID": "3"
        },
        {
          "text": "And all for the countless whorings of the prostitute,",
          "ID": "4"
        },
        {
          "text": "graceful and of deadly charms,",
          "ID": "4"
        },
        {
          "text": "who betrays nations with her whorings,",
          "ID": "4"
        },
        {
          "text": "and peoples with her charms.",
          "ID": "4"
        },
        {
          "text": "Behold, I am against you,",
          "ID": "5"
        },
        {
          "text": "declares the Lord of hosts,",
          "ID": "5"
        },
        {
          "text": "and will lift up your skirts over your face;",
          "ID": "5"
        },
        {
          "text": "and I will make nations look at your nakedness",
          "ID": "5"
        },
        {
          "text": "and kingdoms at your shame.",
          "ID": "5"
        },
        {
          "text": "I will throw filth at you",
          "ID": "6"
        },
        {
          "text": "and treat you with contempt",
          "ID": "6"
        },
        {
          "text": "and make you a spectacle.",
          "ID": "6"
        },
        {
          "text": "And all who look at you will shrink from you and say,",
          "ID": "7"
        },
        {
          "text": "\"Wasted is Nineveh; who will grieve for her?\"",
          "ID": "7"
        },
        {
          "text": "Where shall I seek comforters for you?",
          "ID": "7"
        },
        {
          "text": "Are you better than Thebes",
          "ID": "8"
        },
        {
          "text": "that sat by the Nile,",
          "ID": "8"
        },
        {
          "text": "with water around her,",
          "ID": "8"
        },
        {
          "text": "her rampart a sea,",
          "ID": "8"
        },
        {
          "text": "and water her wall?",
          "ID": "8"
        },
        {
          "text": "Cush was her strength;",
          "ID": "9"
        },
        {
          "text": "Egypt too, and that without limit;",
          "ID": "9"
        },
        {
          "text": "Put and the Libyans were her helpers.",
          "ID": "9"
        },
        {
          "text": "Yet she became an exile;",
          "ID": "10"
        },
        {
          "text": "she went into captivity;",
          "ID": "10"
        },
        {
          "text": "her infants were dashed in pieces",
          "ID": "10"
        },
        {
          "text": "at the head of every street;",
          "ID": "10"
        },
        {
          "text": "for her honored men lots were cast,",
          "ID": "10"
        },
        {
          "text": "and all her great men were bound in chains.",
          "ID": "10"
        },
        {
          "text": "You also will be drunken;",
          "ID": "11"
        },
        {
          "text": "you will go into hiding;",
          "ID": "11"
        },
        {
          "text": "you will seek a refuge from the enemy.",
          "ID": "11"
        },
        {
          "text": "All your fortresses are like fig trees",
          "ID": "12"
        },
        {
          "text": "with first-ripe figs—",
          "ID": "12"
        },
        {
          "text": "if shaken they fall",
          "ID": "12"
        },
        {
          "text": "into the mouth of the eater.",
          "ID": "12"
        },
        {
          "text": "Behold, your troops",
          "ID": "13"
        },
        {
          "text": "are women in your midst.",
          "ID": "13"
        },
        {
          "text": "The gates of your land",
          "ID": "13"
        },
        {
          "text": "are wide open to your enemies;",
          "ID": "13"
        },
        {
          "text": "fire has devoured your bars.",
          "ID": "13"
        },
        {
          "text": "Draw water for the siege;",
          "ID": "14"
        },
        {
          "text": "strengthen your forts;",
          "ID": "14"
        },
        {
          "text": "go into the clay;",
          "ID": "14"
        },
        {
          "text": "tread the mortar;",
          "ID": "14"
        },
        {
          "text": "take hold of the brick mold!",
          "ID": "14"
        },
        {
          "text": "There will the fire devour you;",
          "ID": "15"
        },
        {
          "text": "the sword will cut you off.",
          "ID": "15"
        },
        {
          "text": "It will devour you like the locust.",
          "ID": "15"
        },
        {
          "text": "Multiply yourselves like the locust;",
          "ID": "15"
        },
        {
          "text": "multiply like the grasshopper!",
          "ID": "15"
        },
        {
          "text": "You increased your merchants",
          "ID": "16"
        },
        {
          "text": "more than the stars of the heavens.",
          "ID": "16"
        },
        {
          "text": "The locust spreads its wings and flies away.",
          "ID": "16"
        },
        {
          "text": "Your princes are like grasshoppers,",
          "ID": "17"
        },
        {
          "text": "your scribes like clouds of locusts",
          "ID": "17"
        },
        {
          "text": "settling on the fences",
          "ID": "17"
        },
        {
          "text": "in a day of cold—",
          "ID": "17"
        },
        {
          "text": "when the sun rises, they fly away;",
          "ID": "17"
        },
        {
          "text": "no one knows where they are.",
          "ID": "17"
        },
        {
          "text": "Your shepherds are asleep,",
          "ID": "18"
        },
        {
          "text": "O king of Assyria;",
          "ID": "18"
        },
        {
          "text": "your nobles slumber.",
          "ID": "18"
        },
        {
          "text": "Your people are scattered on the mountains",
          "ID": "18"
        },
        {
          "text": "with none to gather them.",
          "ID": "18"
        },
        {
          "text": "There is no easing your hurt;",
          "ID": "19"
        },
        {
          "text": "your wound is grievous.",
          "ID": "19"
        },
        {
          "text": "All who hear the news about you",
          "ID": "19"
        },
        {
          "text": "clap their hands over you.",
          "ID": "19"
        },
        {
          "text": "For upon whom has not come",
          "ID": "19"
        },
        {
          "text": "your unceasing evil?",
          "ID": "19"
        }
      ],
      "ID": "OT:NAM.3",
      "name": "Nahum 3"
    }
  ],
  "ID": "OT:NAM(ESV)",
  "version": "ESV",
  "name": "Nahum"
}